OL,3,CSelf-confessed 'lazy' couple jailed
OL,4,Cafter children found in squalor
OL,6,FA couple who neglected their two
OL,7,Fchildren and let them live in squalor
OL,8,Fhave been jailed.
OL,10,FJohn Cowley, 37, admitted the home he
OL,11,Fshared with his partner Brooke Carr,
OL,12,F28, on Staveley Street, was an
OL,13,F"absolute dump", South Yorkshire
OL,14,FPolice said.
OL,16,FPolice visited the property in May
OL,17,F2021 after a referral was made by the
OL,18,FNSPCC. Cowley initially refused to let
OL,19,Fthem in, but when they finally gained
OL,20,Fentry, found the house was in a
OL,21,F"disgusting" state.
