OL,3,CSelf-confessed 'lazy' couple jailed
OL,4,Cafter children found in squalor
OL,6,FThe two children were promptly removed
OL,7,Fand have since been placed into foster
OL,8,Fcare.
OL,10,FCowley and Carr were arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of neglect.
OL,13,FAn investigation found they had failed
OL,14,Fto look after the two children's
OL,15,Fhygiene or seek medical assistance for
OL,16,Fillnesses caused by their lack of care.
