OL,3,CSelf-confessed 'lazy' couple jailed
OL,4,Cafter children found in squalor
OL,6,FWhen officers asked Cowley to explain
OL,7,Fthe reason behind the state of the
OL,8,Fhouse, he told them during his
OL,9,Finterview: "I'm not going to sugar-
OL,10,Fcoat it, we were both just pure lazy."
OL,12,FOn Firiday, 19 April, Cowley was
OL,13,Fjailed for two years and three months.
OL,14,FCarr was jailed for two years.
