OL,3,CSelf-confessed 'lazy' couple jailed
OL,4,Cafter children found in squalor
OL,6,FDet Insp Simon Leake said: "We are
OL,7,Fglad the children are now receiving
OL,8,Fappropriate care and support and I
OL,9,Fwould like to commend the hard work of
OL,10,Four partners in helping to gather
OL,11,Fevidence as part of a long running
OL,12,Finvestigation into this case of
OL,13,Fneglect.
OL,15,F"We will continue to protect those who
OL,16,Fare vulnerable and do everything in
OL,17,Four power to bring those responsible
OL,18,Fto justice."
